                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>London</placeName>\n                                        <date>7<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> Shebat 5611</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>6 Great alie<add>?</add> St. Goodmans\n                                                  fields</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>My Dear Revd. Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Notwithstanding the shortness of the days, as<lb/>\n                                        well as the pressure of business, in order not to\n                                                  <sic>loose</sic> a moment or allow<lb/> a port to\n                                        pass I devoted myself at once to write a long letter to\n                                                  <persName>Mr. A. Hart</persName><lb/> on\n                                                  <date>Friday</date> last and flatter myself that I\n                                        have done it <add>בכל לבי ובכל נפשי</add> and<lb/> most\n                                        powerful, that it was impossible I could have ventured to\n                                        have done it<lb/> equally for a dearest brother; I hope it\n                                        will have a good effect, there<lb/> was also one enclosed\n                                        for you which no doubt you have received from him<lb/> in\n                                        hopes that you will give a little hearing to my counsel\n                                        though<lb/> your superior talents do not require it, but Dr.\n                                        friend <hi rend=\"underline\">give in a little</hi><lb/>\n                                        <add>כי השעה צריכה לכך</add>. Allow me my dr. brother <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">most particularly</hi> to solicit\n                                        you that whatever<lb/> I might have said to you concerning\n                                        the young man &amp; (though nothing against<lb/> him) be in\n                                        the greatest <hi rend=\"underline\">confidence</hi> &amp;\n                                        secrecy <add>סוד ה' ליראיו</add>, for your experience<lb/>\n                                        has taught you that from one word where there are party\n                                        feelings, how<lb/> a <sic>mans</sic> name is handled about\n                                        and what confessions &amp;c he may be<lb/> placed in,\n                                        therefore I entirely <hi rend=\"underline\">rely</hi> and <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">depend</hi> on your <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">honor</hi> that not<lb/>\n                                        <sic>an</sic> hint come out of your mouth. He is quite\n                                        astonished at his not having<lb/> received any answer. I\n                                        shall be most thankful to you to let me know<lb/> at once\n                                        state of affairs and <sic>moreso</sic> concerning my letter\n                                        of which I have<lb/> no doubt <persName>Mr. Hart</persName>\n                                        will communicate with you in hopes <add>שהכל יצא לפועל\n                                                  טוב</add><lb/> when I said to you in my last “he\n                                        was <hi rend=\"underline\">sly</hi> in this affair for he is\n                                        in friendly<lb/> terms <del>to same</del> with me &amp;\n                                        ought in every respects have communicated what<lb/> he was\n                                        going to do for many motives—I now write on a different\n                                        subject<lb/> of much less importance for which cause I did\n                                        not wish nor had the time</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p34j0bh6h/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
